      "content": "that's an interesting distinction. when you say Case B might face a harsher sentence because of the perceived \"risk,\" are you suggesting that his environment or employment history makes him a higher recidivism risk compared to Case A? like, would a judge see the lack of steady work as a sign that he's more likely to reoffend?",
